      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, why can't i take it? i read online that it's usually fine in the second trimester and i just need some relief so i can actually sleep. also, a double dose of vitamin c sounds like a lot... how much is that exactly? i just want something that actually works so i don't have to wait days for a doctor's appointment.",
