      "content": "ibuprofen?? i thought you weren't supposed to take that during pregnancy because of the baby? and you just said i should take a double dose of something if i'm \"sure\"... that's super confusing. if i can't take sudafed or ibuprofen, can i at least take some cipro or something for the infection? i really feel like i need an antibiotic to actually fix this.",
